data.description: Beautiful Colonial Home at end of cul-de-sac backs up to Historic property nothing will be built behind you, 1 owner, heated swimming pool,4 bedrooms,basement is insulated and framed.Crown Moulding throughout bottom floor,rear entrance to basement,two car garage,fenced in backyard, gas fireplace insert with blower,Aprilaire media air cleaner.
